abstract: Television ratings for Week 4 of the NFL season beat out the MLB divisional playoffs.
snippet: Ratings for the Giants-Cardinals and the Packers-Broncos games were generally bigger than those for the Yankees-Tigers and the Brewers-Diamondbacks games.
lead_paragraph: Ratings for the Giants-Cardinals and the Packers-Broncos games were generally bigger than those for the Yankees-Tigers and the Brewers-Diamondbacks games.
